Homepage: http://ros.org/wiki/cob_linear_nav
Standards-Version: 3.9.2

Package: ros-hydro-cob-linear-nav
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ros-hydro-actionlib, ros-hydro-move-base-msgs, ros-hydro-nav-msgs, ros-hydro-roscpp, ros-hydro-tf
Description: cob_linear_nav provides a simple navigation instrument driving on a linear path from current position to goal without any planning or obstacle avoidance capabilites. Obstacle avoidance should be carried out in other package, e.g. cob_collision_velocity_filter.
